Exception\"><code>DOMException</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMImplementation\"><code>DOMImplementation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DOMParser\"><code>DOMParser</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPoint\"><code>DOMPoint</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPointReadOnly\"><code>DOMPointReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTimeStamp\"><code>DOMTimeStamp</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Das <strong><code>DOMError-</code></strong>Interface&nbsp;beschreibt ein&nbsp;Fehler-Objekt, welches ein Fehlername enthält.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"eigenschaften","title":"Eigenschaften","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"domerror.name\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>DOMError.name</code></a> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></dt>\n <dd>Gibt ein&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> zurück, welcher einer der&nbsp;folgenden Fehlertypnamen repäsentiert (siehe unten).</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"fehlertypen","title":"Fehlertypen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Typ</td>\n   <td>Beschreibung</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>IndexSizeError</code></td>\n   <td>Der Index ist ausserhalb des gültigen&nbsp;Bereichs&nbsp;(z. B.&nbsp;bei einem&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>range</code></a>-Objekt).</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>HierarchyRequestError</code></td>\n   <td>Die&nbsp;&nbsp;Knoten-Baum-Hierarchie&nbsp;ist nicht korrekt.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>WrongDocumentError</code></td>\n   <td>Das Objekt ist im falschen <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>document</code></a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>InvalidCharacterError</code></td>\n   <td>Der String beeinhaltet unglütige Charakter.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>NoModificationAllowedError</code></td>\n   <td>Das Objekt kann nicht modifiziert werden.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>NotFoundError</code></td>\n   <td>Das Objekt kann nicht gefunden werden.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>NotSupportedError</code></td>\n   <td>Die Operation wird nicht unterstützt</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>InvalidStateError</code></td>\n   <td>Das Objekt hat einen ungültigen Status.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>SyntaxError</code></td>\n   <td><span class=\"hps\">Der String entspricht&nbsp;</span><span class=\"hps\">nicht den erwarteten</span> <span class=\"hps\">Muster.</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>InvalidModificationError</code></td>\n   <td>Das Objekt kann nicht in dieser Art modifiziert werden.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>NamespaceError</code></td>\n   <td>Die Operation ist nicht erlaubt in&nbsp;XML-Namespaces.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>InvalidAccessError</code></td>\n   <td>Das Objekt unterstützt diese Operation oder dieses Argument nicht.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>TypeMismatchError</code></td>\n   <td>Der Typ des Objekts entspricht nicht dem erwarteten Typ.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>SecurityError</code></td>\n   <td>Diese Operation ist unsicher.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>NetworkError</code></td>\n   <td>Ein Netzwerkfehler ist aufgetreten.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>AbortError</code></td>\n   <td>Die Operation wurde abgebrochen.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>URLMismatchError</code></td>\n   <td>Die angegebene URL entspricht nicht einer anderen URL.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>QuotaExceededError</code></td>\n   <td>Das Kontingent wurde überschritten.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>TimeoutError</code></td>\n   <td>Timeout bei der Operation.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>InvalidNodeTypeError</code></td>\n   <td>Der Knoten ist nicht korrekt oder hat falsche Vorfahren für die Operation.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>DataCloneError</code></td>\n   <td>Das Objekt kann nicht geklont werden.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/dom/#interface-domerror\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM4<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'DOMError' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Veraltet</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser-kompatiblität","title":"Browser-Kompatiblität","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basissupport</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>12.0</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basissupport</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>12.0</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Eigenschaften","id":"eigenschaften"},{"text":"Fehlertypen","id":"fehlertypen"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browser-Kompatiblität","id":"browser-kompatiblität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Das DOMError-Interface beschreibt ein Fehler-Objekt, welches ein Fehlername enthält.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"DOMError","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"DOMError","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"DOMError","locale":"fr","nat